{
  "name": "hook-live-progress",
  "createdAt": "2026-07-14T16:41:17.297Z",
  "description": "Add live hook progress streaming so long-running workflow hooks remain observable to both humans and agents while they execute. The change extends the core hook runner and hook progress pipeline, unifies transition and run-hooks presentation through a shared CLI presenter, and finalizes the stdout/stderr split for text versus structured hook output.",
